{"id": 2379, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于搞对象，你都想吐槽哪些老一套的“上世纪观点”？", "description": "那些让你觉得“都啥年代了怎么还这么想”的观点。（题图来自：视觉中国 © TongRO Images）", "record_count": 4408, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180604141935M2saC1SPOhoAx4y7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-06T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 285696, "content": "女人这种生物", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366349}, {"id": 285697, "content": "二十几岁该结婚了！怎么连（男）女朋友都没有！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 285698, "content": "女生能过日子，多干家务", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364459}, {"id": 285699, "content": "感情有啥用 条件好就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325810}, {"id": 286211, "content": "找对象，那叫感触深刻啊，七大姑八大姨的关心，让你体验非凡，逢年过节，父母那更是一个刻骨铭心啊……结婚生子过日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368395}, {"id": 295427, "content": "你为啥不生孩子？\n到了年龄你就该生孩子！\n女人到最后都肯定要生的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 285956, "content": " dj", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186115}, {"id": 285701, "content": "男孩只能跟女孩谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316166}, {"id": 295429, "content": "时间久了都是亲情！所以你现在不要想着找个自己喜欢的他也喜欢你的，只要不讨厌他，就可以在一起！结了婚过日子了再培养感情！那个时候自然就有感情了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 285702, "content": "我是女孩，我爸总会觉得我谈一次恋爱没有成功就是人生的一次摔跤和失误，而女生经不起这种失误...", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366364}, {"id": 285703, "content": "公务员、银行、医生?", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492355}, {"id": 288013, "content": "门当户对，结婚生子\n男主外女主内", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377918}, {"id": 285712, "content": "谈恋爱次数10次以上真的很正常？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724309}, {"id": 285713, "content": "对搞对象没啥印象，我搞过对象吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298133}, {"id": 285714, "content": "女方不止要工作赚钱，也要服侍老公", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078218}, {"id": 285715, "content": "找对象，女生不能太矮，影响下一代，，不能太瘦，不好生养", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078218}, {"id": 289043, "content": "大学的时候:大学里好好学习，不要谈恋爱！\n工作一两年:哎呦，怎么还没有男朋友啊？", "image": "img/option/option/201806251037458OvpfqWSnPMmI2gJ", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383056}, {"id": 285716, "content": "帅有什么用，长得好看的都不踏实。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366409}, {"id": 285717, "content": "父母说，找个老实本分的就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333885}, {"id": 285718, "content": "男方家在哪就要在哪落户工作？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363453}, {"id": 285719, "content": "有网恋的没？需求:女生\nQQ:1974170149", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366429}, {"id": 285721, "content": "年纪不小啦，赶紧找一个吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 285722, "content": "你为什么还不找男朋友啊？你为什么不谈恋爱呀?  -关你屁事", "image": "img/option/option/20180606144728WlcbrX3ajLTVzMsZ.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317469}, {"id": 290075, "content": "我们都替你着急啊，快结婚吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342659}, {"id": 285724, "content": "以结婚为基础的搞对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345916}, {"id": 286237, "content": "剩女\n（遗憾的是很多女生也这样叫自己）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361926}, {"id": 285726, "content": "女孩儿到了25岁就该结婚安家 不然以后老了怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337027}, {"id": 288799, "content": "22岁前谈恋爱会被乱棍打死，然而25不结婚已经是老姑娘的眼光看你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 285728, "content": "“我们不接受你就休想谈。”?", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308174}, {"id": 286496, "content": "所有以己度人，把自己的婚恋观念强加到别人头上的说辞都是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361167}, {"id": 285729, "content": "“感情能当饭吃吗？”?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308174}, {"id": 287267, "content": "私企？那就是打工，就是没工作。\n爸妈感情不好？等着被戴绿帽子吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920897}, {"id": 285732, "content": "随缘恋爱法了解一下！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359418}, {"id": 287012, "content": "找女朋友找个屁股大的好生儿子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373161}, {"id": 285735, "content": "女孩子做个老师就不错～", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358356}, {"id": 285736, "content": "成熟了，再谈对象，可每次还是一身伤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357158}, {"id": 286509, "content": "看完之后觉得我的父母好开明", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371284}, {"id": 285998, "content": "女孩子一定要结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353511}, {"id": 285743, "content": "脸不重要，关了灯都一样，胖点好，有福气", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366478}, {"id": 285746, "content": "女方就要顾家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363308}, {"id": 285747, "content": "女生就要做家务，女生就要做饭，生活就要靠女方，男生就应当在外赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363308}, {"id": 285748, "content": "一定要搞对象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932603}, {"id": 286260, "content": "为什么我喜欢的我妈不喜欢\n我妈得意的我不得意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368702}, {"id": 285749, "content": "不能太矮，看着不搭", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366511}, {"id": 285750, "content": "长大之后深刻理解“门当户对”。然而还是搞不懂长辈那一套，什么属鸡的不要和属狗的结婚，“鸡犬不宁”什么的！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96454}, {"id": 287033, "content": "洒家命犯天煞孤星，自己瞎几把过吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103270}, {"id": 288825, "content": "当然有很重要的一点就是看不起我们LGBTQ了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380842}, {"id": 285754, "content": "女孩子做家务是应该的，不会做饭，不勤快就一定会被婆婆嫌弃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723340}, {"id": 285755, "content": "三大件。。。男的要高要富有车有房，彩礼钱要一分钱不少！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036991}, {"id": 286268, "content": "所谓“早恋”，小孩子懂什么叫喜欢？还有“同性恋”就是变态！你怎么还能支持？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362853}]}